title: Fleeting Circus
description:
fleeting circus aims to create a different kind of music than the one produced in Brazil, looking forward to reaching a global audience. This project started in 2011, putting together a large variety of musical and artistic genres, such as Post-Rock, Art Rock, Neo-psychedelia, Electronica and even circus performances.
 
The name Fleeting Circus is a blend of satire and criticism, regarding sensationalist press and media. 

Songs in this album:

 * Look for Greener Fields
 * Dancing Tides
 * Pino
 * Favourite Illusion
 * On the Road to Innocence
 * Skylight
 * Ghost Writer
 * Cornucopia
 * Adrift
 * The Master
